Text: A woman was sitting at a bar enjoying an afterwork cocktail with her girlfriends when an exceptionally tall handsome extremely sexy young man entered He was so striking that the woman could not take her eyes away from him The young man noticed her overlyattentive stare and walked directly toward her Before she could offer her apologies for being so rude for staring the young man said to her Ill do anything absolutely anything that you want me to do no matter how kinky for on one condition Flabbergasted the woman asked what the condition was The young man replied You have to tell me what you want me to do in just three words The woman considered his proposition for a moment withdrew from her purse and slowly counted out four bill which she pressed into the young mans hand along with her address She looked deeply into his eyes and s l o w l y meaningfully said CLEAN MY HOUSE Join the worlds largest email service with MSN Hotmail

I checked the email that went out for girls weekend and Amy Gold was first on the list I dont think Ive heard back from her or if I have her name didnt make it to the rsvpd list So find out if shes coming Ill put Sam down as no J Chat with friends online try MSN Messenger

Girls WeekendSounds like almost everyone can make the weekend It will be fun Ready for your food assignments Well here they are Friday Dinner If you get there by pm we will be going out to eat We might leave a note on the door telling you where we are If you get there later you are on your own for dinner but Lisa promises to leave the door unlocked and the light on for you The dog doesnt bite too hard Saturday Breakfast Sam and Lee Saturday Lunch Well be going down to Kemah for lunch drinks by the bay and shopping If youre not up for it you can stay at home by the pool and relax while we gossip about you Saturday Dinner Cynthia Paula and Phyllis make it lite please Sunday Breakfast Kim and Janell Snacks Judy Lisa and Oni As usual everyone should bring drinks enough for one A few wine bottles would be delightful also Lisa says she has plenty of paper products but Im not sure she has enough toilet paper for all of us for the weekend so throw some of that in your bag too if you have extra at home Call me if you have questions The next Girls Weekend will be November th pm through November th At Lisa Polks house Bay Oaks Blvd Houston Texas Janell email address Janell otmailcom phone Get Your Private Free Email from MSN Hotmail at Share information about yourself create your own public profile at

Fwd FW the next Girls WeekendMark your calendars Pack your bags Gas up the car The next Girls Weekend is scheduled When April Place Marble Falls Texas Let me know by return email if you think you can come Ill get back with you on all the specifics driving directions what to bring and that ever important topic FOOD and WINE If youd like to spend a bit longer in Marble Falls Phyllis can accommodate Thursday arrivals and Monday departures Just let me know so we can reserve your bed Some members of the group have been having a difficult time lately so lets all get together and be supportive of each other For all mobile members of the group some shopping in Fredricksburg is available on Saturday Looking forward to seeing all of the you Janell PS Should your email address suddenly change for whatever reason be sure to keep in contact with me phone From Warner Cynthia A To Janell otmailcom Janell otmailcom Subject FW the next Girls Weekend Date Wed Jan Hi there Since you have the most current email list and are a pro at organization heres some info for the next Girls Weekend I just talked to Phyllis and shes ready to go with April She mentioned she will be around the Thursday before and until Monday noon after in case anyone wants a little more time She also mentioned a Fredericksburg excursion on Saturday and she also has a friend that wants to come Talk to you soon Cyn Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday January PM To Warner Cynthia A Subject Re the next Girls Weekend Great to hear from you Yes on the Girls Weekend I have been thinking I needed to get a note out to everyone but I didnt Anyway I think the weekend of April would be great I dont think it interferes with the MS which was a conflict for Judy How should we go about this project Also I think we might consider availability as early as Thursday evening and at late as Monday morning since there is a bit more travel involved Phyllis Send and receive Hotmail on your mobile device

From Cynthia Warner Personnel Secretary to Janell Dye Hi Girls Im visiting Janell and Dennis this weekend She still has a gimpy leg and cant make it upstairs to their computer She asked me to send some info on Girlss Weekend Unfortunately she is doubtful that she will make it this time Heres the scoop Girls Weekend is still on for November December at Lisas inlaws place on the Bolivar Pennisula Lisa will be sending directions and a phone If you are receiving this email we are assuming you are coming Janell is requiring Christmas pictures Kim please bring your camera Judy please bring your aerobed just in case we need it with sheets and a blanket Bring a deck chair Food assignments will be coming Lisa I volunteered us to come up with them Friday night you are on your own for dinner In case its cold you may want to bring a blanket Janell says hi she is waving her crutch and is looking forward to the next gathering See you soon Cynthia Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at intlasp

Rome reservationsAttached is your reservation for Rome for September This room is charged to your Amex account but the reservation is in my name Print this attachment out and take it with you since it has the confirmation on it You will have a king nonsmoking deluxe room at per night including breakfast This probably isnt in the downtown area since it is supposedly a golf resort Paul said he would find out the exact location for us If you are able to locate something better feel free I could find several hotels on Travelocity that had availability but the phone wasnt provided and you can only book one room at a time The cancellation policy on this hotel is good we just have to cancel by pm Sept so we can easily switch hotels Talk to you later J Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at intlasp
